Wagner Labor Archives <lb/>Elmer Holmes Bobst Library <lb/>70 Washington Square South <lb/>New York, NY 10012, New York University Libraries.
Donated by the Actors' Fund of America in several donations between 1985 and 2007. The accession numbers associated with this collection are 1985.020, NPA.2007.001, NPA.2008.005, and NPA.2009.022.
The Actors Fund. <emph render="italic">Curtain Call: 125 Amazing Years of the Actors Fund</emph>. Virginia Beach, VA: Donning Company Publishers, 2008.
<emph render="bold">Series XI: Audiocassettes (1986-1995)</emph>, consists of tapes of meetings, pressconferences events and sound clips of Lillian Gish and Emma Zale.
